File,storm,com,offers,a,free,and,a,premium,file,hosting,service,Using,the,FileStorm,API,requires,users,to,have,an,API,key,This,can,be,obtained,by,creating,an,account,The,API,allows,users,retrieve,file,information,or,upload,files,themselves,To,access,any,information,on,the,site,other,than,very,basic,API,info,an,account,must,be,created